A tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020, cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ta karu sosai a cikin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai (EU) / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EEA) da Burtaniya.
Shafin na Cigaban Cutar Coronavirus (COVID-19) ya nuna cewa akwai irin wannan yanayin a cikin Tarayyar Turai / Kasashen da ke da iyaka da ke da iyaka da Burtaniya, kuma ya tabbatar da cewa cutar ta COVID-19 tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe, a cikin matakai daban-daban dangane da ƙasa.
Dangane da kwarewar da aka samu a Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa mai mahimmanci ya kamata su haɓaka shirye-shiryen su don karuwar masu cutar COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an ba da rahoton bayyanar cutar huhu da ba a san dalilin cutar ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Kula da Cututtuka ta China ta ba da rahoton gano wani abu da ke haifar da cutar Novel Coronavirus, wanda yanzu ake kira da mummunar cutar numfashi ta coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta haifar ana kiranta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
A yau, akwai tabbacin cewa kusan kashi 80 cikin 100 na waɗanda ke da cutar COVID-19 sun kamu da cutar huhu, amma ba cutar huhu ba, amma sun kamu da cututtukan numfashi masu sauƙi, kuma mafi yawansu sun warke.
A cikin kusan kashi 14 cikin dari na cutar, COVID-19 ta canza zuwa wani yanayi mai tsanani wanda ke buƙatar asibiti, kuma a cikin sauran kashi 6 cikin dari, an sami mummunan rashin lafiya wanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai mahimmanci.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kashi 4 cikin dari.
A cikin wannan binciken, za mu bincika yanayin yiwuwar yaduwar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya ta ƙasa kuma mu kwatanta su da China da Hubei.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a yanzu a cikin Tarayyar Turai (EU) / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EEA) da Burtaniya da kuma adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu da 15 ga Maris, 2020.
An samu karin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a EU/EEA da Birtaniya
Bayan barkewar cutar a China, COVID-19 ya ci gaba da yaduwa zuwa wasu yankuna, kuma cutar ta COVID-19 ta yi tashin gwauron zabi a sauran ƙasashe a duniya.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cewar ma'anar barkewar cutar ta WHO, an tabbatar da farkon cutar COVID-19 a cikin mutanen Turai, kamar yadda aka bayyana a cikin mujallar likitanci ta Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al., a ranar 5 ga Maris.
An gano mutane uku na farko da suka kamu da cutar a cikin EU/EEA a Faransa a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020, wadanda suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano cututtukan COVID-19 a cikin kasashe 30 na Tarayyar Turai (EU) / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EEA) da Burtaniya (UK), tare da samun karuwar masu kamuwa da cutar 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019, da kuma a cikin Italiya, wanda ya kai mutane 17,750 da suka kamu da cutar tare da mutuwar 1,441.
Samun adadin yaduwar COVID-19 da kuma yawan yaduwar cutar
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC) tana sabunta bayanan COVID-19 kowace rana da karfe 8:00 na safe, daga ma'aikatun kiwon lafiya na ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki, da kuma daga tushen hukuma kamar WHO.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanin don kimanta yiwuwar yanayin COVID-19 a EU/EEA da Burtaniya da kuma kwatanta yanayin ƙasashen da yanayin Italiya.
A matsayin samfurin sake fasalin yanayin COVID-19 na yanzu, mun ƙididdige adadin sake fasalin yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya a cikin kwanaki 14 da sama da haka daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020, kuma muna ɗaukar shi azaman ma'aunin COVID-19.
Mun kuma bayyana adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a kowace kasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8:00 na safe, idan aka kwatanta da adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu da 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
A cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata, yawan masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai (EU) / EEA da Burtaniya sun yi daidai da yawan masu kamuwa da cutar a lardin Hubei na kasar Sin (Hoto 1).
Idan aka duba duk EU/EEA da Burtaniya, ƙididdigar sake dawowar COVID-19 ta fara tashi a kusan 21 ga Fabrairu, sannan ta yi ƙaruwa sosai a kusan 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (a cikin ƙarin bayani).
Wannan ya samo asali ne daga karuwar adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar a Italiya, wanda ya nuna irin wannan karuwar a cikin cutar COVID-19 a duk ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai (EU) / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EEA) da Burtaniya (bayanai na gaba).
Hoto na 2 ya kwatanta karuwar adadin cututtukan COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya da Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Bayan makonni uku da ƙasa, sauran ƙasashe 15 na Tarayyar Turai (EU) / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EEA) da Burtaniya sun ba da rahoton adadin adadin waɗanda suka kamu da cutar a Italiya a ranar 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00 na safe.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 yana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya.
Bayanan da aka lura da su na COVID-19 sun nuna cewa cutar tana karuwa a cikin daidaito a duk ƙasashe.
A cikin ƙasashe, ayyukan lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa suna kan matakai daban-daban, a cikin yanayi daban-daban, kuma duk da bambance-bambance a cikin ƙasashe daban-daban a cikin ƙayyadaddun ƙididdigar cutar da kuma hanyoyin da ake buƙata don zaɓar marasa lafiya don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da haɗakar gwaji, har yanzu suna ci gaba.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta bulla a Italiya sun bayyana cewa kusan kashi 10 cikin 100 na marasa lafiya da ke dauke da cutar COVID-19 na bukatar kulawa mai tsanani, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun bayyana cewa asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa mai tsanani a yankunan sun kai matakin karbar marasa lafiya.
A matakin Tarayyar Turai (EU) / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EEA), kashi 6% da 1% na yawan marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da ke asibiti da/ko cibiyoyin kulawa mai tsanani ne kawai ke da damar (ba a bayyana bayanan ba).
Amma, ya kamata a yi bincike a kan su a cikin tsari don ƙarfafa bayanan da ake da su na yanzu, wanda ke mai da hankali kan adadin masu cutar da kuma mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka gudanar a shekarar 2010-11 ya gano cewa adadin gadaje na kulawar gaggawa da kulawar lokaci-lokaci a Turai ya bambanta sosai daga ƙasa zuwa ƙasa, inda Jamus ke da gadaje 29.2 a kowace mutane 100,000, yayin da Portugal ke da gadaje 4.2 kawai.
Wannan yana nufin cewa suna da albarkatu da yawa kuma ba su da yawa fiye da Italiya (wanda ke da gado 12.5 na kulawa mai mahimmanci da kulawa mai matsakaici a cikin mutane 100,000 a cikin 2010-11).
An haɗa yanayin tunanin da aka tsara wanda ke da alaƙa da wadatar kulawar lafiya a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya tare da ƙididdigar sake kamuwa da cutar a cikin marasa lafiya da ke cikin asibiti na COVID-19 waɗanda ke da haɗarin ƙetare &gt; 90% na ƙwayoyin cuta masu saurin kulawa da ke da alaƙa da ƙimar kulawa mai mahimmanci a cikin ƙasashe na EU / EEA da Burtaniya a cikin sabuntawa ta shida na ECDC na Saurin Binciken Hadarin COVID-19.
Saboda cutar tana da yawa a cikin wasu yankuna na EU/EEA da Burtaniya, kuma asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da gaggawa suna iya kula da ƙididdigar yawan jama'a, ya kamata a samar da bayanai game da barkewar cutar da kuma yawan kulawar gaggawa ga cibiyoyin kula da gaggawa na yankin don ƙididdigar ƙididdiga na matakin 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da kuma damar da ake da ita a yanzu a wasu ƙasashe suna nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya.
Saboda haka, ya kamata kasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa na musamman suyi shiri don sarrafa yaduwar cutar SARS-CoV-2 a yankin da kuma karuwar adadin marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman, kamar yadda ya faru a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya.
A cikin rahoton da ECDC ta yi kwanan nan, an nuna cewa, don jinkirta yaduwar SARS-COV-2, ana buƙatar saurin, shiri da kuma ingantaccen tsarin kula da cutar, tare da sauyawa daga hanawa zuwa sauƙaƙa. Idan yawan masu haƙuri ya ƙaru kamar yadda aka zata, rashin shiri na gaba na iya haifar da rashin isasshen lokaci ga masu yanke shawara da asibitoci don fahimtar yanayin cutar da amsawa yadda ya kamata.
A cikin wannan rahoton, an bayyana matakan kiwon lafiya na jama'a don rage lalacewar cutar.
Akwai damar da za a iya ba da ta gajerun lokuta don ƙasashe su ƙara haɓaka ƙoƙarin sarrafa su don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba a kan kiwon lafiya.
Idan ba mu yi nasara ba, tsarin kiwon lafiya na sauran kasashen EU / EEA na iya fuskantar karuwar marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa mai mahimmanci a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar Coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce ke haifar da cutar ta numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV-2), ta kashe mutane sama da 3,000 a China da sauran sassan duniya, kuma ta haifar da bala'i ga bil'adama.
SARS-CoV-2 wanda ya yi kama da kwayar cutar SARS, wanda ya haifar da cutar SARS a cikin dubban mutane a 2003, na iya zama mai cutar daga ɓeraye, yana haifar da halaye iri ɗaya ta hanyar irin wannan ɓangaren.
Koyaya, COVID-19 yana da ƙarancin ƙarfi da ƙarancin mutuwa fiye da SARS, amma yana da saurin yaduwa, yana cutar da tsofaffi fiye da matasa, kuma yana cutar da maza fiye da mata.
A cikin martani ga saurin rubuce-rubuce game da cutar da ke tasowa, an yi ƙoƙari a cikin wannan labarin don samar da cikakken bayani game da abubuwan bincike masu saurin canzawa.
Za mu yi aiki don hada abubuwa kamar nazarin annoba, binciken dalilin cutar, nazarin kwayar cutar, ganewar asali, magani, kimantawa da rigakafin cutar.
Duk da yake akwai tambayoyi da yawa da har yanzu ake bukatar amsa, muna fatan wannan bita zai taimaka wajen fahimtar cutar da kuma kawar da ita.
Bikin bazara da aka yi a ranar 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya zama abin tunawa ga duk Sinawa waɗanda aka bukaci su zauna a gida tsawon makonni a lokacin hutu da kuma bayan hutu saboda barkewar cutar coronavirus.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta sanya masa suna SARS-CoV-2, kuma ta sanya sunan cutar da ke da alaƙa da cutar COVID-19 (COVID-19), saboda kwayar cutar ta yi kama da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) da ta haifar da barkewar cutar numfashi mai tsanani (SARS) a 2003.
Cutar ta fara ne a birnin Wuhan na kasar Sin kuma ta yadu cikin sauri a duk fadin kasar Sin da kuma kasashe kusan 50 a duniya.
Ya zuwa ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta haifar da sama da mutane 80,000 da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19, sama da 40,000 aka sallame su daga asibiti, kuma sama da 3,000 sun mutu.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 shine babban makiyin jama'a kuma yana iya zama mai ƙarfi fiye da ta'addanci.
Rahoton farko na binciken kwayar cutar bayan warewar marasa lafiya da yawa, kamar yadda aka bayyana a PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), an gabatar da shi ne a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020, kuma a cikin watanni biyu, an buga sama da takardu 200 da suka shafi binciken cutar, nazarin annoba, bincike kan dalilin cutar, ganewar asali da magani na COVID-19.
Wannan bita ya yi ƙoƙari ya taƙaita bincike na ci gaba a kan sabon yanki mai saurin canzawa.
A duk lokacin da zai yiwu, za mu gwada COVID-19 da SARS da sauran cututtukan da ke haifar da CoV, da kuma cutar numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, annoba da ta barke a shekarar 2012).
Za mu tattauna duk abin da muka sani game da rigakafin cutar da kuma yadda za a iya yin hasashen cutar, da kuma wasu batutuwan da suka rage.
CoVs sune kwayoyin cuta waɗanda ba su da haɗari ga mutane, galibi suna haifar da kimanin kashi 15% na yanayin sanyi na matakin 4.
Amma a wannan karni, mun gano sau biyu cewa mutane suna da cutar coronavirus: SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, wanda ya fara a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabia a 2012, kuma nan da nan ya bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe tare da mummunan ƙimar kamuwa da cuta da mutuwar.
Saboda haka, annobar COVID-19 ta yanzu ita ce ta uku ta CoV a tarihin ɗan adam.
An fara ba da rahoton wani mummunan fashewar cutar huhu ta sanyi da ba a san asalinsa ba a Wuhan ga Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta China a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019.
Bayan kwana bakwai, an sanar da sakamakon cutar.
An ba da rahoton mutuwar farko a Wuhan a ranar 15 ga Janairu, 2020.
A halin yanzu, annobar ta bazu cikin sauri zuwa garuruwa, jihohi da ƙasashe masu iyaka.
A ranar 20 ga watan Janairu, an sanar da cewa ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya sun kamu da cutar, kuma an yi la'akari da cewa ana iya yada cutar daga mutum zuwa mutum.
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, an dakatar da duk hanyoyin sufuri na jama'a a Wuhan kuma an kulle birnin.
A ranar 24 ga watan Janairu, binciken farko na cutar ya gano cewa daga cikin mutane 41 da aka tabbatar da cutar, 21 ne suka yi tafiya zuwa kasuwar abincin teku ta Wuhan, inda ake ganin cutar ta samo asali ne daga dabba da ba a bayyana sunanta ba.
A ranar 30 ga watan Janairu, WHO ta ayyana barkewar cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta duniya.
A lokacin da aka fitar da wannan rahoto, cutar ta riga ta bazu a duk fadin kasar Sin da kuma kusan wasu kasashe 50 a duniya (Hoto na 2).
Yanayin yana ci gaba da canzawa, kuma har yanzu ana bukatar tantance ƙarshen yaduwar cutar da kuma tsananin cutar.
A cewar wani bincike na cibiyoyi da dama da aka gudanar a kan marasa lafiya 8,866 da suka hada da 4,021 da suka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, ana samun cikakken bayani game da cutar a wannan hanyar.
SARS-CoV-2 na iya kamuwa da cutar a kowane zamani, amma yawanci ana kamuwa da ita ne tsakanin shekaru 30 zuwa 65.
