Kwayoyin jini na T, ciki har da CD4 + da CD8 + T, suna taka muhimmiyar rawa wajen hana cutar.
CD4 + T cells suna motsa B cells don samar da kwayoyin cutar anti-virus, yayin da CD8 + T cells ke kashe kwayoyin cutar kai tsaye.
Kwayoyin T masu taimako suna samar da sitokin mai kumburi don taimakawa ƙwayoyin da ke kare su.
