A ranar 11 ga Maris, Firayim Minista Conte ya ba da umarnin dakatar da kusan dukkan kasuwancin, sai dai manyan kantuna da kantunan magunguna. A ranar 6 ga Maris, Kwalejin Kula da Magunguna, Magunguna da Kula da Gaggawa da Maidowa ta Italiya (SIAARTI) ta buga shawarwarin ɗabi'a na likita game da kulawar mai haƙuri mai mahimmanci, wanda ya kamata a yi amfani da shi.
A ranar 19 ga watan Maris, Italiya ta samu mutuwar mutane 3,405 sakamakon kamuwa da cutar, inda ta zarce China a matsayin kasar da ta fi kowacce mutuwa a duniya sakamakon cutar coronavirus.
A ranar 22 ga watan Maris, an sanar da cewa Rasha ta tura jiragen sama 9 na soja dauke da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya zuwa Italiya.
A ranar 5 ga Afrilu, Italiya ta sami mutane 128,948 da suka kamu da cutar, 15,887 sun mutu, kuma 21,815 sun warke, mafi yawan su a yankin Lombardy.
Rahoton CNN ya nuna cewa yawan tsofaffi a Italiya da rashin gwajin cutar a kan lokaci ne ke haifar da hauhawar mutuwar.
A lokacin da cutar ta fara bulla, Burtaniya ta kasance cikin kasashe da ta fi kowa jin dadi a cikin kasashen da cutar ta shafa, kuma har zuwa ranar 18 ga Maris, 2020, gwamnatin Burtaniya ba ta aiwatar da kowane nau'i na nisantar jama'a ko sanya ido kan 'yan kasarta ba.
A sakamakon haka, an soki gwamnatin saboda jinkirin mayar da martani ga halin da al'umma ke ciki. A ranar 16 ga Maris, Firayim Minista Boris Johnson ya ba da shawarar dakatar da tafiye-tafiye marasa mahimmanci da duk fannonin zamantakewa, da yin aiki daga gida idan ya yiwu, da kuma guje wa shaguna, gidajen cin abinci da gidajen wasan kwaikwayo.
A ranar 20 ga Maris, gwamnati ta sanar da cewa za ta rufe duk kantunan da ke buɗe don nishaɗi kamar mashaya da filin wasa da wuri-wuri kuma za ta biya ma'aikata har zuwa £ 2,500 a wata da kashi 80% na albashi don hana rashin aikin yi a lokacin annobar. A ranar 23 ga Maris, Firayim Minista ya ba da sanarwar cewa ya ga ya zama dole a bi tsauraran matakan nisantar da kai, ƙuntata taron mutane sama da biyu, da kuma ƙuntatawa kan tafiya da fita waje.
A wani bangare kuma, 'yan sanda sun yi amfani da wannan dokar ta hanyar tara kuɗi da kuma raba mutane daga taron jama'a.
An kuma umarci a rufe yawancin kasuwancin da ake ganin suna bukatar ci gaba da budewa, ciki har da manyan kantuna, kantin sayar da magunguna, bankuna, kantin sayar da kayayyaki, kantin sayar da man fetur da kuma wuraren gyaran motoci.
A ranar 20 ga watan Janairu, an tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 ta farko a yankin Pacific Northwest na jihar Washington, namiji ne wanda ya dawo daga Wuhan a ranar 15 ga watan Janairu.
A ranar 29 ga watan Janairu, an kafa Kwamitin Kula da Cutar Korona na Fadar White House.
A ranar 31 ga watan Janairu, gwamnatin Trump ta ayyana dokar ta baci ta kiwon lafiya ta jama'a kuma ta sanya takunkumi kan shigowar masu yawon bude ido daga China.
A ranar 28 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Gwamnatin Amurka ta sanar da cewa sun kirkiro na'urar gwajin kansu.
Duk da haka, yana da wahala a san yanayin cutar a lokacin saboda jinkirin da Amurka ta yi wajen gudanar da gwajin.
Gwajin bai yi tasiri ba saboda rashin ingantattun kayan aikin da gwamnatin tarayya ta bayar a watan Fabrairu. Gwamnatin tarayya ba ta ba da izinin kayan aikin gwaji daga kungiyoyi masu zaman kansu (masana kimiyya, makarantu, jami'o'i) ba har zuwa ƙarshen Fabrairu, wanda ke buƙatar mutane su cika ka'idoji don yin gwaji har zuwa farkon Maris (kuma ya buƙaci amincewar likita).
Washington Post ta ruwaito cewa a ranar 27 ga watan Fabrairu, kasa da gwaje-gwaje 4,000 ne kawai aka gudanar a Amurka.
A ranar 13 ga watan Maris, jaridar The Atlantic ta ruwaito cewa an kammala gwajin gwajin kasa da 14,000.
A ranar 22 ga watan Maris, AP News ta ce, mutane da yawa da ke da alamun cutar sun jira sa'o'i ko kwanaki don yin gwaji. Bayan mutuwar farko a Amurka, a ranar 29 ga watan Fabrairu, Washington ta ba da rahoton cewa Gwamna Jay Inslee ya ayyana dokar ta baci.
Makarantu a yankin Seattle sun soke azuzuwan su a ranar 3 ga Maris, kuma an rufe makarantu a duk faɗin ƙasar a tsakiyar watan Maris. Wani rukunin masu ilimin cututtukan cuta a Kwalejin Imperial ta London sun ba da shawarar hasashen tasirin sabon coronavirus a kan ƙasar a Amurka a ranar 6 ga Maris, 2020.
A wannan ranar, Shugaba Trump ya sanya hannu kan Dokar Saurin Shirye-shiryen Coronavirus da Amsa, wanda ke ba da dala biliyan 8.3 a cikin kudaden gaggawa ga hukumomin tarayya don magance barkewar cutar.
Manyan kamfanoni suna sanya takunkumin tafiye-tafiye ga ma'aikata, soke tarurruka, da kuma karfafa ma'aikata su yi aiki daga gida.
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, Trump ya sanar da dakatar da tafiye-tafiye zuwa mafi yawan Turai, ban da Burtaniya, na tsawon kwanaki 30 daga ranar 13 ga watan Maris.
A rana mai zuwa, ya tsawaita takunkumin zuwa Burtaniya da Ireland.
A ranar 13 ga watan Maris, ya ayyana dokar ta baci a fadin kasar, wanda hakan zai sa a fara amfani da kudaden tarayya wajen magance bala'i.
Tun daga ranar 15 ga watan Maris, an rufe ko rage lokutan aiki a kamfanoni da dama a fadin Amurka don rage yaduwar cutar.
A ranar 17 ga watan Maris, an tabbatar da bullar cutar a duk jihohi 50 da gundumar Columbia. A ranar 23 ga watan Maris, an bayar da rahoton cewa New York City tana da mutane 10,700 da ke dauke da cutar coronavirus, wanda ya fi adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar a Koriya ta Kudu.
Gwamnan ya ce a ranar 25 ga Maris, ana ganin cewa nisantar jama'a na aiki, saboda an ga cewa adadin masu kamuwa da cutar ya ninka sau biyu daga kwanaki 2.0 zuwa 4.7.
A ranar 28 ga watan Maris, New York City ta samu mutane 32,308 da suka kamu da cutar, kuma 672 sun mutu sakamakon cutar. Amurka ta ba da rahoton a ranar 26 ga watan Maris cewa ta fi kowace kasa a duniya, ciki har da China da Italiya, yawan wadanda suka kamu da cutar coronavirus.
A cewar wani rahoto na kafofin watsa labarai a ranar 30 ga Maris, Shugaba Trump ya yanke shawarar tsawaita dokar nisantar jama'a har zuwa 30 ga Afrilu.
A wannan ranar ne aka ajiye jirgin asibiti na Amurka mai dauke da gadaje 1,000 a New York.
A ranar 3 ga Afrilu, an sami rikodin mutuwar mutane 884 a cikin awanni 24 a Amurka.
A jihar New York, adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar ya kai sama da 100,000 a ranar 3 ga Afrilu. Fadar White House ta fuskanci hukunci saboda rashin kula da hadarin, da sanarwar jama'a ga jami'an kiwon lafiya da masana kimiyya game da cutar, da kuma umarnin yin hulɗa da haɗin gwiwa tare da ofishin mataimakin shugaban kasa Mike Pence a cikin watsa labarai.
An raba jam'iyyun biyu game da goyon bayan da Trump ya samu game da yadda ya magance matsalar.
Wasu jami'an Amurka da wasu kafofin yada labarai sun soki dogaro da shigo da kayayyakin gaggawa daga China, ciki har da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya da ake bukata.
An yi amfani da tsarin tafiye-tafiye na iska don tsara taswirar wuraren da cutar ta yadu da kuma kimanta yanayin kamuwa da cuta, kuma an buga wannan bincike a cikin mujallar Travel Medicine a tsakiyar watan Janairu na 2020.
Bayanai na 2018 na Kungiyar Kula da Sufurin Jiragen Sama ta Duniya sun nuna cewa Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo da Taipei sune manyan wuraren da fasinjoji suka fi yawa daga Wuhan.
An kuma bayar da rahoton cewa Dubai, Sydney, da Melbourne sune wuraren da mutane ke zuwa daga Wuhan.
An sanar da tsibirin Bali cewa ya kamata ya kasance a cikin manyan wurare 20 da ke da matukar bukatar kiyayewa yayin da biranen Australiya ke buƙatar kiyayewa. Australia ta ba da sanarwar shirin gaggawa na sabon coronavirus (COVID-19) a ranar 7 ga Fabrairu.
Ba a samu ƙarin bayani game da COVID-19 ba, kuma Australia ta ce za ta ƙarfafa kula da kan iyakoki da sadarwa a matsayin martani ga annobar.
A ranar 21 ga watan Maris, an ayyana dokar ta baci ta lafiyar dan adam a Australia.
Da yake akwai ingantaccen sa ido kan sufuri na jama'a a Wuhan da Hubei, kasashe da dama sun shirya fitar da 'yan kasarsu da ma'aikatan diflomasiyya daga yankin, da farko ta hanyar jiragen haya zuwa kasashen su na asali, tare da samun izinin hukumomin kasar Sin.
Kanada, Amurka, Japan, Indiya, Sri Lanka, Australia, Faransa, Argentina, Jamus da Thailand sun fara shirin kwashe 'yan kasarsu zuwa inda suka fi aminci.
Pakistan ta ce ba za ta dauki mataki ba don dawo da 'yan kasarta da ke cikin kasar Sin.
A ranar 7 ga watan Fabrairu, gwamnatin Brazil ta sami damar kwashe 'yan kasar Poland hudu, da wani dan kasar Sin, da kuma wani dan Indiya, da kuma wasu 'yan kasar Brazil 34 ko kuma danginsu.
A lokacin da jirgin ya tsaya a wani wuri kafin ya koma Brazil, 'yan kasar Poland, China da Indiya sun sauka daga jirgin.
An killace 'yan Brazil da suka ziyarci Wuhan a wani sansanin soji kusa da Brasilia.
A cikin kwana daya, 'yan Kanada 215 (176 daga jirgin farko da gwamnatin Amurka ta yi haya, da 39 daga na biyu) an sanya su a cikin sa ido na makonni biyu daga Wuhan zuwa CFB Trenton.
A ranar 11 ga watan Fabrairu, wani jirgin sama daga Wuhan dauke da 'yan Kanada 185 ya sauka a filin jirgin sama na CFB Trenton.
A ranar 3 da 4 ga watan Fabrairu, hukumomin Australiya sun kai 'yan kasar 277 zuwa wani wurin da ake tsare da su a tsibirin Kirsimeti, wanda aka sake fasalin shi a matsayin wurin da ake tsare da cutar, inda suka zauna tsawon kwanaki 14.
Jirgin ceto na New Zealand ya isa Auckland a ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, kuma fasinjojin (ciki har da wasu 'yan asalin Australiya da wasu daga kasashen Pacific) an killace su a sansanin Sojan Ruwa na Whampawera a arewacin Auckland.
A ranar 15 ga watan Fabrairu, Amurka ta sanar da cewa za ta kwashe Amurkawa daga jirgin ruwan Diamond Princess zuwa inda ba su da lafiya.
A ranar 21 ga watan Fabrairu, wani jirgin da ke dauke da fasinjoji 129 na 'yan Kanada da ke cikin jirgin Diamond Pricess ya sauka a garin Trenton, Ontario.
A farkon watan Maris, gwamnatin Indiya ta fara kwashe 'yan kasarta daga Iran zuwa inda suke lafiya. A ranar 14 ga watan Maris, jirgin kamfanin jiragen sama na Afirka ta Kudu da gwamnatin Afirka ta Kudu ta yi haya ya dawo da 'yan Afirka ta Kudu 112.
An gudanar da gwajin lafiya kafin tashi, kuma an bar 'yan Afirka ta Kudu huɗu da ke nuna alamun cutar coronavirus don rage haɗarin.
An mayar da 'yan Afirka ta Kudu ne kawai da suka yi gwajin lafiya kuma suka sami lafiya.
A matsayin mataki na farko, an gwada dukkan 'yan Afirka ta Kudu marasa cutar, ciki har da dukkan ma'aikatan jirgin, matukan jirgi, ma'aikatan otal,' yan sanda da sojoji, waɗanda suka shiga cikin aikin sadaukarwa na kwanaki 14 a The Ranch Resort.
A ranar 20 ga watan Maris, Amurka ta fara janye wasu daga cikin dakarunta daga Iraki saboda annobar.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, ma'aikatar harkokin wajen kasar Sin ta ce kasashe 21 (ciki har da Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad da Tobago, Masar da Iran) sun ba da tallafi ga kasar Sin.
Wasu daliban kasar Sin da ke halartar jami'o'in Amurka sun ce sun hada kai a fadin yankin Chicago don kai agaji zuwa yankunan da cutar ta addabi inda suka samu nasarar isar da kayan rufe fuska N95 guda 50,000 zuwa asibitocin lardin Hubei a ranar 30 ga watan Janairu. A hadin gwiwa da kungiyar agaji ta FedEx, kungiyar agaji ta bayar da 200,000 na kayan rufe fuska tare da wasu kayan kariya na mutum, ciki har da safofin hannu da riguna, zuwa asibitin lardin Wuhan a ranar 30 ga Janairu.
"A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Bill da Melinda Gates sun sanar da cewa sun ba da gudummawar dala miliyan 100 ga WHO don samar da rigakafi da kuma hanyoyin magance cutar da za ta iya hana "masu fama da cutar a Afirka da Kudancin Asiya".
A ranar 6 ga watan Fabrairu, Sanata Richard Gordon ya ba da gudummawar abin rufe fuska 200,000 ga Philippines bayan da ya aika da abin rufe fuska miliyan 3.16 zuwa Wuhan, a cewar rahoton Ineraksyon.
A ranar 19 ga watan Fabrairu, kungiyar 'yan ci-rani ta Singapore ta sanar da cewa za ta aika da kayayyakin agaji da suka kai dala miliyan 2.26 zuwa kasar Sin.
Japan ta ba da gudummawar abin rufe fuska miliyan daya ga Wuhan, Turkiyya ta ba da kayan aikin likita, Rasha ta aika da kayan aikin likita sama da tan 13 zuwa Wuhan, Malaysia ta sanar da bayar da gudummawar safar hannu na likita miliyan 18 ga China, Jamus ta ba da kayan aikin likita iri-iri, ciki har da rigunan Hersem 10,000, Amurka ta ba da gudummawar kayan aikin likita tan 17.8 ga China, kuma ta yi alkawarin ba da ƙarin dala miliyan 100 na taimakon kuɗi ga ƙasashen da abin ya shafa. Lokacin da al'amuran suka daidaita a China, China ta ba da taimako ga ƙasashe da yawa da cutar ta shafa.
A watan Maris, China, Cuba da Rasha sun aika da kayan aikin likita da masana zuwa Italiya don magance yaduwar cutar coronavirus.
Jammar, wani dan kasuwa, ya aika da kayan gwaji miliyan 1.1, da abin rufe fuska miliyan 6 da rigunan kariya 60,000 zuwa Addis Ababa, Habasha, don rarraba daga Tarayyar Afirka.
Daga baya ya aika da kayan gwaji 5,000, abin rufe fuska 100,000 da na'urorin numfashi biyar zuwa Panama.
Ma ya kuma ba da gudummawar kayan aikin likita ga Kanada. Kasashen Netherlands, Spain, Turkiyya, Georgia da Jamhuriyar Czech sun nuna damuwarsu game da abin rufe fuska da kayan gwajin da aka yi a China.
Misali, a Spain, an dawo da na'urorin gwajin cutar coronavirus 58,000 na kasar Sin tare da daidaito na kashi 30 cikin dari, yayin da a Netherlands, an dawo da abin rufe fuska 600,000 na kasar Sin tare da lahani.
A Belgium, an dawo da abin rufe fuska 100,000 da ba su dace da amfani ba, abin da ake tsammanin daga China ne, amma a zahiri daga Colombia ne.
A wani bangare kuma, kasashen Latin Amurka da Afirka na karbar kayan agaji daga China. A ranar 2 ga watan Afrilu, Bankin Duniya ya fara shirin samar da agaji na gaggawa ga kasashe masu tasowa.
Hukumar ta WHO ta ba da shawarar cewa hukumomin kasar Sin su gudanar da kokarin da suke yi na shawo kan annobar.
"WHO ta lura da wani muhimmin bambanci tsakanin hukumomin China, wadanda ake zargi da yin ɓoye-ɓoye da suka jinkirta ayyukan rigakafi da sarrafawa a lokacin barkewar cutar SARS ta 2002-2004, da kuma gwamnatin tsakiya, wacce ke sakin bayanai na yau da kullun kafin hutun Sabuwar Shekarar Sin don "guje wa firgita" a lokacin rikicin na yanzu".
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, yayin da yake mayar da martani kan shawarar da hukumomin tsakiya suka yanke na aiwatar da dokar hana zirga-zirga a Wuhan, wakilin WHO Gordon Gallia ya yi sharhi cewa, "Tabbas ba shawarar WHO bane". Ya kuma ce, "Wannan muhimmin alama ne na ƙudurin sarrafa annobar a wuraren da aka fi taruwa", inda ya kira ta "marasa misali a tarihin ɗan adam". Bayan tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar a cikin mutane a waje da China a ranar 30 ga Janairu, da kuma lokacin da cutar ta bazu a cikin wasu ƙasashe, WHO ta bayyana cutar a matsayin babbar matsalar lafiyar jama'a, kuma ta kasance farkon lokacin PIC a cikin 2009.
"Darakta Janar na WHO Tedros Edhanwan ya ce sanarwar PHEIC "ta zama mai wahala saboda yiwuwar barkewar cutar a duniya, musamman a ƙasashe masu ƙarancin kuɗi da matsakaitan kuɗi waɗanda ba su da ingantaccen tsarin kiwon lafiya".
Tedros ya amsa da cewa, "babu wani dalili da zai sa a dauki matakan da za su iya tsoma baki ba dole ba a tafiye-tafiye da cinikayya ta kasa da kasa", kuma ya ce, "WHO ba ta bayar da shawarar hana kasuwanci da tafiye-tafiye ba".
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO ta nemi al'umma ta duniya da ta ba da dala miliyan 675 don tallafawa shirye-shiryen dabarun a ƙasashe masu ƙarancin kuɗi.
Tedros ya fitar da sanarwa inda ya ce "za mu iya zama masu karfi a cikin mafi rauninmu" kuma ya bukaci al'umma ta duniya da su "sanya hannun jari a yau, in ba haka ba za a biya mai girma a wani lokaci". A wani taron manema labarai a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta ba da sunan cutar COVID-19.
A wannan rana, Sakatare Janar na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya António Guterres ya amince da bayar da "ikon da dukkan tsarin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ke da shi" don taimakawa wajen mayar da martani, in ji Tedros.
An kafa kungiyar kula da hadarin ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda ya ba da damar hadin gwiwar amsawar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya baki daya. Kasashe membobin WHO sun ba su damar mai da hankali kan mayar da hankali kan martani na kiwon lafiya yayin da sauran hukumomi ke kawo ƙwarewarsu don magance tasirin zamantakewa, tattalin arziki da ci gaba da ya haifar da barkewar cutar.
A ranar 14 ga watan Fabrairu, an kafa wata kungiya ta hadin gwiwa da kasar Sin karkashin jagorancin WHO, tare da masana na kasa da kasa da na WHO a kan lamarin, don taimakawa kasar Sin wajen gudanar da aikin gida, da kuma gudanar da bita da bita kan yadda ake fuskantar tsananin cutar da kuma yaduwar cutar a manyan cibiyoyin kasa da bita da tarurruka, da kuma gudanar da nazarin filin kan tasirin ayyukan da ake yi a matakin gunduma da birni, ciki har da na birni da na karkara. A ranar 25 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO ta fara sanar da cewa duniya ta fi son yin shiri don cutar ta coronavirus, kuma ta ce, idan cutar ta zama annoba, ta yi iya ƙoƙarin da ta dace, ta ce, "ya kamata kasar ta yi a matakin shiri".
A sakamakon karuwar yaduwar cutar a Iran, WHO ta tura tawagar hadin gwiwa zuwa Iran don kimanta halin da ake ciki. A matakin duniya, jami'an WHO sun ce matakin barazanar na iya tashi daga kashi 10 zuwa 10 cikin 100 a matakin annobar, kuma ya kasance mafi girma a matakin gargadi da kimanta hadari.
Myrin, darektan gudanarwa na shirin gaggawa na kiwon lafiya na WHO, ya yi gargadin wani ra'ayi na yanzu: "Akwai abu daya da kowane gwamnati a duniya ke bukatar ta sarrafa: Tashi".
"Kwayar cutar tana kan hanyarta, kuma kuna buƙatar kasancewa a shirye", ya yi kira ga duniya da ta dauki matakan da suka dace don kauce wa "mafi munin yanayi".
Ryan ya kara da cewa, "bayanan da muke da su yanzu ba su da inganci sosai don jami'an kiwon lafiyar jama'a su ayyana cutar a matsayin annoba ta duniya, kuma yin hakan zai nuna cewa mun yarda da cewa duk mutane a duniya za su kamu da cutar".
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana cutar coronavirus a matsayin annoba.
Darakta Janar ya ce WHO na da matukar damuwa game da yadda cutar ta kai matakin da ya kamata a kula da shi, da kuma yadda ake samun karancin adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar. An yi ta sukar WHO kan rashin isasshen matakan da ta dauka wajen shawo kan annobar, ciki har da jinkirin ayyana dokar ta baci ta kiwon lafiya da kuma jinkirin ayyana cutar a matsayin annoba.
A ranar 6 ga watan Afrilu, mutane 733,000 suka sanya hannu a kan bukatar da ake yi na yin murabus daga mukamin daraktan WHO Tedros Adhanom.
A ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020, masana 'yancin dan adam na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sun jaddada muhimmancin girmama hakkin dan Adam na kowane mutum a lokacin annobar COVID-19.
Kungiyar ta ce kowa na da hakkin samun taimakon da zai ceci ransa, kuma gwamnati ce ke da alhakin hakan.
Kungiyar ta jaddada cewa rashin albarkatu ko inshorar lafiya bai kamata ya zama dalilin nuna bambanci ga wasu mutane ba.
Masana sun jaddada cewa kowane mutum yana da hakkin samun lafiya, ciki har da masu nakasa da kuma wadanda ke cikin kananan kungiyoyi, tsofaffi, 'yan gudun hijira marasa gida, marasa gida, wadanda ke cikin matsanancin talauci, wadanda ke tsare, amma kuma 'yan gudun hijira da sauran kungiyoyi marasa tsari da ke bukatar tallafin gwamnati.
Hukumomin duniya suna magance tasirin tattalin arziki da zamantakewar rikicin COVID-19.
Kungiyar hadin gwiwar tattalin arziki da ci gaba ta kirkiro wani dandamali don samar da cikakken bayani da kuma ra'ayoyi kan manufofin mayar da martani a cikin kasashe daban-daban a duniya.
Daga tsara manufofi don ƙarfafa tsarin kiwon lafiya da tattalin arziƙin duniya zuwa magance tasirin kulle-kulle da ƙuntatawa kan tafiye-tafiye, cibiyar dijital ta ƙunshi tsarin sa ido kan manufofin ƙasa, wanda ke nufin taimakawa ƙasashe suyi nazari da juna da kuma sauƙaƙe haɗin kai na duniya game da ƙalubalen coronavirus.
Eduardo Bolsonaro, dan shugaban Brazil, Gabriel Sanaro, Ministan Harkokin Wajen Birtaniya, Michael Golff, da Amurka sun zargi gwamnatin China kan yadda ta magance annobar cutar a lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
