b'Angiotensin-converting enzyme2 (ACE2) wani enzyme ne wanda ke mannewa da farfajiyar kwayoyin da ke cikin huhu, jijiyoyin jini, zuciya, koda da hanji.
ACE2 yana da matukar amfani wajen magance cututtukan zuciya da jijiyoyin jini saboda yana hana aikin enzyme mai canza Angiotensin (ACE) ta hanyar rage matakin Angiotensin-II da kuma kara yawan Ang (1-7). ACE2 kuma yana aiki a matsayin hanyoyin shiga cikin kwayar halitta ga wasu coronaviruses.
An fi kiran wannan enzyme a cikin mutum hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 wani nau'in zinc ne wanda ke dauke da metallloenzyme wanda ke zaune a cikin endothelial da sauran kwayoyin halitta.
Kwayar ACE2 tana dauke da yankin N-terminal peptidase M2 da kuma yankin C-terminal collectrin na jigilar amino acid na koda.
ACE2 shine furotin mai wucewa guda ɗaya na nau'in I wanda yake aiki akan farfajiyar ƙwayoyin cikin huhu da sauran ƙwayoyin cuta tare da yankin da enzyme ya kunna.
An cire yankin waje na ACE2 daga yankin a cikin membrane ta wani enzyme da ake kira sheddase, kuma furotin mai narkewa da aka samar yana gudana cikin jini kuma daga ƙarshe ya fita cikin fitsari.
